name: Festive Flame
desc: When this card is Normal Summoned: You can send to the GY, from the top of your opponent's Deck, cards equal to the number of cards your opponent controls. If this card is Special Summoned: You can send to the GY, from the top of your Deck, cards equal to the number of cards your opponent controls. You can only use this effect of “Festive Flame” once per turn.
